00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:56,490
You weren't there.
你当时不在场！

150
00:09:57,160 --> 00:10:00,360
No, but, you know, it's just a funny image.
是不在，但想想都好笑

151
00:10:00,530 --> 00:10:05,990
You know, the two of you in this restaurant with the..
想想你们两个 在这个餐馆，还...

152
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:12,730
Ross, why don't you tell Benji about your proposal while I go to the ladies' room.
罗斯 我去洗手间的时候你能告诉本你的方案吗？

153
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,300
So tell me about it.
来吧，告诉我吧。

154
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:20,910
Okay. Well, I would like to do a dig in the Painted Desert.
我们会在沙漠里进行挖掘.

155
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:24,280
There are still several areas that haven't been fully excavated.
因为里面还有些地区还没完全开挖的。

156
00:10:24,450 --> 00:10:25,780
