-乔伊，我们不能留着这个！ -但它是原版的布费作品啊...

306
00:21:03,290 --> 00:21:06,020
All right, fine. You can keep it.
好的，没关系，你就留着吧。

307
00:21:06,190 --> 00:21:08,560
As long as you don't mind that she's haunted.
只要你不介意她周围游荡。

308
00:21:08,730 --> 00:21:10,250
Hey, what? What?
嘿？什么？什么？嘿！噢！什么！？

309
00:21:10,660 --> 00:21:15,190
Well, legend has it, Joey, that she comes alive when you're asleep.
有这样一个传说...她在半夜里会活过来。

310
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:20,500
She climbs out of the frame..
她爬出这画框

311
00:21:20,670 --> 00:21:24,970
and then drags her half-a-body across the floor..
然后她拖着她这半个身体，爬在地板上

312
00:21:25,150 --> 00:21:26,980
just looking for legs to steal.
想办法去偷一双腿

313
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:30,780
And then with her one good hand..
然后她用她唯一的一只手

314
00:21:30,950 --> 00:21:34,910
she slowly reaches up..
慢慢、慢慢地

315
00:21:35,090 --> 00:21:37,320
and turns your doorknob.
扭开门把手

316
00:21:37,490 --> 00:21:41,290
Get that legless witch out of here!
拿走这没脚的妖怪！！

317
00:21:46,730 --> 00:21:49,900
- Hey, I sold that to Joey. - Yeah, well, I told him it's haunted.
-嘿！我把它卖给乔伊了！ -所以我骗他这是鬼怪了

318
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:52,900
- Two can play at this game. - Too late. You can't give it back.
-我们都会玩这种把戏 -不行，太迟了，你不能退货！

319
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:55,270
- Oh, yes, I can. - No, you can't, she's yours.
-我当然可以！ -不，你不可以，她是你的 ！

320
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,840
- She's yours. - She's yours.
-她是你的！ -是你的！

321
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:59,410
- She's yours. - Hey.
-她是你的！ -嘿！

322
00:22:00,950 --> 00:22:02,470
- She's mine. - She's mine.
-她是我的！ -是我--的！

323
00:22:02,650 --> 00:22:04,510
- She's mine. - She's mine.
-她是我的！ -她是我的！

324
00:22:04,690 --> 00:22:07,920
You guys, you don't have to fight over her anymore.
你们啊！不用为她争吵了。

325
00:22:08,320 --> 00:22:11,520
Whoever doesn't get Gladys, gets Glynnis.
谁得不到格拉达斯，就把格林妮斯拿回去吧。

326
00:22:19,730 --> 00:22:21,890
- I want Gladys. - She's mine.
-我要格拉达斯。 -她是我的！

327
00:22:22,070 --> 00:22:24,060
- She's mine. - She's mine.
-她是我的！ -她是我的！

328
00:22:31,850 --> 00:22:33,470
No, no. You don't get to do that.
不要不要.你们不要这样了

329
00:22:33,650 --> 00:22:36,950
I know. Look, I'm sorry I didn't give them your tape.
很抱歉我没有把你的带子给他们。

330
00:22:37,120 --> 00:22:41,140
And I promise next time to submit you, whether I think you're right or not.
我保证，下次无论合不合适我都会把你推荐上去的。

331
00:22:41,320 --> 00:22:44,310
That's not the point, Chandler. The point is that you lied.
重点不是这个啊钱德。 重点是，你说了谎

332
00:22:44,490 --> 00:22:49,090
I know. You're right. What's it gonna take for you to forgive me?
我知道，你说的对 我要做什么你才能原谅我？

333
00:22:49,260 --> 00:22:50,320
Oh, my God.
噢 天啊！

334
00:22:54,600 --> 00:22:56,660
Excellent.
无得弹！

335
00:22:57,600 --> 00:23:00,040
Now what do you say?
现在你该说什么？

336
00:23:00,210 --> 00:23:02,400
Lying is wrong.
说谎是不对的！

337
00:23:02,580 --> 00:23:05,070
And? And?
还有呢？...还有呢？

338
00:23:06,850 --> 00:23:09,610
I'm a pretty little girl.
我是个漂亮美眉。

339
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:12,720
I knew it.
我早就知道啦！

340
00:23:20,360 --> 00:23:23,690
Your ex-boyfriend is insane.
你的前男友是个疯子。

341
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:26,230
- He is a character. - No, no, no.
-他是个有个性的人 -不是, 才不是呢

342
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:29,490
Charles Nelson Reilly is a character.
查尔斯・纳尔逊・赖利才是

343
00:23:30,070 --> 00:23:32,540
- Who? - Charles Nelson Reilly.
- 谁? - 查尔斯・纳尔逊・赖利

344
00:23:32,710 --> 00:23:35,830
The Ghost and Mrs. Muir? Match Game?
The Ghost and Mrs. Muir? Match Game?（两个电影名）

345
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:39,840
Were you never sick as a child?
你小时侯都没得过病吗?

346
00:23:40,610 --> 00:23:43,810
- Whatever. Did you get the grant? - No. And you wanna know why?
- 随便啦！ 你得到那笔补助了吗？ - 没有，你想知道为什么吗？

347
00:23:43,980 --> 00:23:47,250
Because your ex-boyfriend is still in love with you.
因为你的前男友还是爱着你。

348
00:23:47,420 --> 00:23:48,450
- What? - Yeah.
-什么？ -没错

349
00:23:48,620 --> 00:23:50,990
He refused me because I wouldn't give you up.
他没有给我那笔补助，就因为我没有放弃你。

350
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:54,420
Benji isn't in love with me. I mean, he broke up with me.
本不会还爱着我的。 因为当时是他抛弃我

351
00:23:54,590 --> 00:23:58,930
- And besides, he's a very ethical man. - Really?
-而且，他是个认真的人。 -是吗？？？

352
00:23:59,670 --> 00:24:02,430
Is it ethical to ask someone in a grant review:
在补助调查中问这种问题：

353
00:24:02,600 --> 00:24:04,470
"Who was the voice of Underdog?"
“谁是Underdog（电影名）的配音员？”  很认真吗？

354
00:24:05,310 --> 00:24:06,860
I'm sure he was just joking.
我肯定他是在开玩笑，罗斯。

355
00:24:07,040 --> 00:24:09,240
If you don't believe me, let's go talk to him.
如果你不相信我，我们去找他对质吧。

356
00:24:09,410 --> 00:24:12,470
I'm telling you, he didn't ask me one paleontological question.
可以告诉你 他没有问过我一个关于考古学的问题

357
00:24:12,650 --> 00:24:15,580
- Seriously? - Oh, I'm sorry. No, he did ask me one:
-真的吗？ -哦，不是，他问了我一个。

358
00:24:15,750 --> 00:24:18,080
"How do you spell Boscodictiasaur?"
呃...怎么拼Mboscodictiosaur

359
00:24:18,250 --> 00:24:21,780
Well, if it's like the Lake Mbosco in Congo, then M-B-O..
和刚果的Mbosco湖拼法一样，那是M-B-O...

360
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:23,120
Damn it.
可恶！

361
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:29,990
Dr. Geller. Charlie, what are you doing here?
盖勒博士...？查莉  你...你到这来干什么？

362
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:32,060
I want you to tell her everything.
我要你告诉他一切。

363
00:24:32,230 --> 00:24:35,900
About the deal you tried to make with me, about the crazy questions you..
告诉他你想和我做的交易，那些神经病的问题

364
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:41,370
Wally Cox. That's the voice of Underdog.
沃利・考克斯！他就是Underdog的配音！

365
00:24:42,180 --> 00:24:44,270
Like I tried to tell you in the interview..
就如之前的调查我告诉你一样

366
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:48,380
this grant is not based on your knowledge of pretty useless trivia.
这个补助基金不是为了这些无聊的知识而设的

367
00:24:48,550 --> 00:24:53,510
No, don't do that. I want you to look her in the eyes and tell her the truth.
不！不！不！别这样！ 我要你看着她的眼睛，告诉她真相。

368
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:55,850
Benji?
Benji?

369
00:24:57,060 --> 00:25:01,890
All right. It's true. I behaved horribly, but it's only because I still love you.
是的，的确是这样。我之前简直是乱来。 但这都是因为我还爱着你。

370
00:25:02,060 --> 00:25:05,000
And I would do anything to have you back in my life.
只要你回到我身边，我可以做任何事。

371
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:07,830
Too little, too late, Benji.
太少了，太迟了，Benji！

372
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:13,030
- I can't believe this. - I never should've broken up with you.
-我不敢相信。 -我真不应该离开你

373
00:25:13,210 --> 00:25:18,230
I think about you all the time. Do you ever still think about me?
我无时无刻不想起你。 难道你一点都没有想起我?

374
00:25:18,410 --> 00:25:19,900
No.
没有!

375
00:25:20,780 --> 00:25:23,110
- Yes. - What?
-有! -什么?

376
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:27,880
I don't know what to say, Benji. This is all so..
我不知道该说什么好了，Benji。 这一切实在太...

377
00:25:28,050 --> 00:25:30,110
romantic.
浪漫了

378
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:32,150
Or?
或者...

379
00:25:34,900 --> 00:25:37,090
I know I may be way out of bounds here..
我知道，或者我做得太过火了

380
00:25:37,260 --> 00:25:40,720
but is there any chance you would take me back?
但我们还有机会在一起吗？

381
00:25:43,270 --> 00:25:45,400
Maybe.
或者可以...

382
00:25:45,570 --> 00:25:49,470
Sweetie, this conversation is starting to make me a little uncomfortable.
甜心，你们的对话让我觉得有点不舒服了。

383
00:25:51,140 --> 00:25:54,910
Oh, God. I am so sorry, but..
噢 天啊！我很抱歉，但...

384
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:59,850
I mean, there's so much history between us, you know?
我是说...我们之前有太多的过去了...

385
00:26:00,050 --> 00:26:02,520
I'm sorry too.
我也觉得抱歉...

386
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:14,290
- I love you. - I love you too.
-我爱你! -噢! 我也爱你!

387
00:26:16,270 --> 00:26:19,330
Okay, that's it, we are seeing other people.
好了, 够了。我们算是完了！

388
00:26:39,090 --> 00:26:40,080
Gladys?
格拉达斯?

389
00:26:47,130 --> 00:26:50,900
For the third time this week. Man, this does not get old.
哈哈哈，这个星期的第三次了。 老兄，你怎么还没长大啊？

